{"tid":1565321,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普開除博爾頓 聚焦對付中共","createTime":"2019-09-13T05:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T06:02:49.000Z","uid":78570,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d76f98830ca67090e016c63ba290e5dfae1d6632","tid":1565321,"uid":78570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:58:35.000Z","msg":"分析指，博爾頓是個對中東和俄羅斯的鷹派，不符合川普打擊美國的頭號敵人中共的戰略。川普此前公開表示，自己被選中挑戰中共，將不惜代價迎擊中共。<br />\n<br />\n最近，博爾頓還建議川普不要同塔利班會晤，以完成結束阿富汗戰爭的談判。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯俄 中共大事不妙<br />\n有消息透露，博爾頓被解雇後，中共馬上發動各種隱藏力量進行遊說，試圖將自己中意的人選推上這個重要職位。而川普中意的人選將是一名真正的反共鬥士。<br />\n<br />\n全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/19/9/12/n11517208.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F19%2F9%2F12%2Fn11517208.htm&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QQRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=9df98f8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/19/9/12/n11517208.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3ddb3105dc3ad509214cbe80a2509f1a2f8eb912","tid":1565321,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:59:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"30489c7278e2aafb1c63830aa2f1ddbcb325010c","tid":1565321,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:59:08.000